www.investing.com/analysis/eurusd-back-to-the-bottom-200471785 EUR/USD: Back To The Bottom? By By Scott Barkley | 3 hours ago (Oct 09, 2019 11:21AM ET)

Follow EUR/USD Bearish : Currently we are @1.0977 in a range. We are looking to continue to the Day chart bottom @ 1.0863. Watch for the reaction there back to the range bottom or a break out to the 1.270 Fibo @ 1.0736. The 14-day ATR (Average True Range) is 57 Pips with a 180-day ATR of 56 Pips.
